                <note rend="inline" type="source">814.00/1199: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Guatemala</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hanna</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-05-04T14:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 4, 1935—2 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>13. Your 17, May 2, noon. In view of the short time before the Constituent
                    Assembly will meet the Department wishes you to telegraph the specific points on
                    which you desire the Department’s views.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
